The,Chicago,Open,API,provides,connectivity,between,government,authorities,and,residents,in,the,City,of,Chicago,The,API,that,is,anchored,on,the,Open,platform,facilitates,feedback,communication,on,a,variety,of,issues,such,as,potholes,falling,within,the,jurisdiction,of,the,city,s,government,A,developer,must,first,request,a,test,API,key,and,deploy,it,in,Open,system,s,test,environment,to,be,able,to,access,the,production,API,key,The,Chicago,Open,API,generates,calls,in,HTTP,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,JSONP,and,XML,formats